toolchain, initramfs and scripts to help you build your kernel
build environment should be:
[build-folder]
    /sgs-kernel
    /initramfs
    /arm-eabi
    build.sh
    clean.sh

initramfs scmversions:
SGS GT-I9000:
-I9000XXJVP-CL264642
-I9000XXJVQ-CL281085

SGS2 GT-I9100:
-I9100XWKF3-CL276555

to build the kernel, put your version inside build.sh and execute ./build.sh from your [build-folder]